# Format the commit message as follow:
#
# Title
# Empty line
# Body
#
# Title:: <action>[scope]: <description>
# Where 
# - Action:
#   [add, remove, update]
# - Scope:
#   [homebrew, shell, packages, casks, apps, mas, drivers, fonts, screensavers, quicklook]
# - Description
#   Short description
#
# Body:: [Optional]
#
# -----